com.facebook.litho.widget

Interface MountableCharSequence

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CharSequence

    public interface MountableCharSequence
extends CharSequence
    Mountable CharSequence that is aware when the Text component using this CharSequence is mounted and unmounted.
    See Also:
